blubber (0.3.0-1) unstable; urgency=medium

  [ Tyler Cipriani ]
  * dh-golang: exclude vendor directories

  [ Dan Duvall ]
  * Docker env for Debian packaging on non-Debian systems
  * Resolve variant includes with the correct ordering
  * Fix application files/runtime permissions scheme
  * Simplify Docker instruction compilation
  * Generalize instructions for entrypoint and working directory

  [ Tyler Cipriani ]
  * Makefile: install to global GOPATH with correct -ldflags

  [ Dan Duvall ]
  * Support Python projects
  * Allow for configuration policies
  * Fix ownership on artifact copies
  * Provide a `runs.insecurely` to be used with test variants

  [ Tyler Cipriani ]
  * No need to export NewValidator
  * Policy example should work on blubber.example.yaml

  [ Dan Duvall ]
  * Release v0.3.0

